translations: n.吸虫（fluke 的复数形式）；锚爪
v.侥幸成功（fluke 的第三人称单数）

sentences.sentence: I'm not sure if my results are flukes.
sentences.translation: 我不确定我的结果只是偶然现象。

sentences.sentence: "We're proud of our record of flukes," De Fina says.
sentences.translation: “我们为我们创下的侥幸成功记录感到骄傲，”德·菲纳说。

sentences.sentence: I probably shouldn't say it but some of the best things have been flukes.
sentences.translation: 可能我不该这样说但是一些好的玩意儿并不是侥幸成功的。
